---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contributing | 20th Century Democide">
	<section class="stack">
		<div class="panel">
			<p class="kicker">Contributing</p>
			<h1>Preservation work should be auditable, incremental, and source-based.</h1>
			<p>
				Open pull requests for source recovery, metadata corrections, and normalization improvements. Keep
				editorial intervention outside the preserved body text and include provenance for every substantive
				change.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="panel">
			<h2>Recommended flow</h2>
			<ol>
				<li>Update the relevant manifest entry.</li>
				<li>Capture or recover the raw source.</li>
				<li>Record hashes and source metadata.</li>
				<li>Normalize into Markdown only after the raw capture is stable.</li>
				<li>Run <code>npm run validate</code>.</li>
			</ol>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
